The leaders of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) from the Oke Ogun region have announced Chairman, Oyo State Housing Corporation, Bayo Lawal, as the running mate of Governor Seyi Makinde for the 2023 election, The Nation reports. The meeting was attended by Governor Makinde; Oyo PDP chairman Kunmi Mustapha; Chairman State Advisory Council Senator Hosea Agboola, party leaders, elders, and leaders from the Oke Ogun region. The announcement was made after a closed-door meeting of the stakeholders at the Presidential Lodge, Government House, Agodi, Ibadan on Tuesday.